Zip file contains an .exe that opens with:   Thank you for downloading this file. Increasing server costs forced us to implement a new system that requires your participation before we unlock your download. Your file will remain locked until you fill the offer below. It takes only less than one minute to complete and it will greatly help us to keep our servers free.

When filling offer please use your real information (confirmation required), otherwise "Unlock" button will remain disabled. Thank you :)

Fuck this bullshit.
